text:
:mega:Hey <!subteam^S06HNNE4YQ0|@team>:mega:

Welcome back everyone and get excited for our upcoming *DTI Halloween party*!!:ghost: Below are some details:dti::dti::dti::
• :bangbang:DTI will be hosting our annual halloween party in collaboration with CDS:bangbang:
    ◦ :date:When: Saturday 10/25 @10:30PM
    ◦ :round_pushpin:Where: 131 N Quarry St, Ithaca, NY, 14850
    ◦ :ghost:Who: YOU (FREE) and your potential plus one (ALSO FREE)
• Please <https://partiful.com/e/u1KZPN6fVSWcH6Vpaspa|RSVP> here and include your plus one if needed by Thursday 10/23 for headcount. Those who don’t rsvp by the deadline will not be able to enter.
• For additional plus ones -> we ask for a $3 fee to help with costs.
• Additionally, we need your help with *volunteering* to keep this event safe and fun for *1 TEC*!! Roles include door duty, set up and cleaning. Please fill out this <https://forms.gle/kBMXrM9Te1LpAwg69|volunteer form> if you are interested or message <!subteam^S03R8V9GMCN|@business-leadz>.
• There will be a separate channel created next week to send out more details
:bangbang:BRING YOUR COSTUMES, FRIENDS, AND LETS HAVE FUN TOGETHERRR WITH CDS:bangbang:
